  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class GeoFenceIntentService
extends android.app.IntentService
    An IntentService subclass for handling asynchronous task requests in a service on a separate handler thread. This service is invoked whenever a geofence transition happens, and handles the transition and takes the required actions
